370
00:23:41,120 --> 00:23:41,760
Brother.

371
00:23:42,390 --> 00:23:44,840
I'm so excited!

372
00:23:45,190 --> 00:23:46,520
I'm so excited!

373
00:23:46,710 --> 00:23:47,320
He...

374
00:23:47,320 --> 00:23:49,600
