finally get together happily.

548
00:34:35,910 --> 00:34:37,320
After a breakup and reconciliation,

549
00:34:37,470 --> 00:34:39,910
Xiaobu and Fang Lie,

550
00:34:40,030 --> 00:34:42,760
two young lovebirds,

551
00:34:42,760 --> 00:34:45,800
