00:35:10,240 --> 00:35:11,030
It's salty.

564
00:35:31,910 --> 00:35:33,030
Your mouth.

565
00:35:45,910 --> 00:35:46,590
Wipe it.

566
00:35:48,680 --> 00:35:49,280
This...

567
00:35:52,070 --> 00:35:52,990
This...

